<div class="modal fade" id="heightHelp" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLongTitle" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered" role="document">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <font class="modal-title" id="exampleModalLongTitle">Height of Each Color Tile Section</font>
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                    <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                </button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                This model assumes you will be switching colors at specific layer heights of your print.
                For example, if you are printing a pendant and you select "0.3", then you print your backing from 0 - 2.0mm,
                your grey tiles from 2.0 - 2.3mm, your yellow tiles from 2.3mm - 2.6mm and then finally your green tiles from 2.6 - 2.9mm
                <p>
                    <table cellpadding="3" cellspacing="3" width="100%">
                        <tr valign="top">
                            <td><img src="@Url.Content("~/Content/Images/CrossSectionForPrinting.png")" alt="Cross Section for Printing" /></td>
                            <td>
                                <strong>Pendant with 0.3mm "Height of Each Color Tile Section"</strong>
                                <table border="1">
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>Correctly Placed Letters (Green)</td>
                                        <td>2.6mm - 2.9mm</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>Misplaced Letters (Yellow)</td>
                                        <td>2.3mm - 2.6mm</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>Wrong Guesses (Grey)</td>
                                        <td>2.0mm - 2.3mm</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>Backing (White)</td>
                                        <td>0.0mm - 2.0mm</td>
                                    </tr>
                                </table>

                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
